<font color="#FF0000">RESCUING NUNGS</font><br>
<tt>Thu Jun  5 23:42:23 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
John,<br>
     I caught an SOS post from a Green Beret group on the Dinky Dau Express 10 days ago that identified these Vietnamese as Nungs who had all served in various capacities with the Green Berets.  The post had requested any concerned vets to try and generate some congressional pressure on the State Dept. to get involved in these cases ASAP as possible deportation to Vietnam was imminent.  Called VVA National to request that they weigh in.  Don't know if I was successful, but everything seems to be turning out all right.
<p><code>-- gerald_ney@icpphil.navy.mil  (Gerald Ney &quot;professor&quot;, 7/68-7/69) </code><p>


